OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1779706980
OL,3,CCumbria's James Trafford and Dean
OL,4,CHenderson selected for England World
OL,5,CCup team
OL,7,FCockermouth's James Trafford and
OL,8,FWhitehaven's Dean Henderson have been
OL,9,Fselected for England's World Cup squad.
OL,11,FEngland manager Thomas Tuchel unveiled
OL,12,Fhis line up on Friday 22 May.
OL,14,FBoth Trafford and Henderson are
OL,15,Fgoalkeepers.
OL,17,F23-year-old James Trafford, who was
OL,18,Fborn in Cockermouth and grew up in the
OL,19,Fnearby village of Greysouthen, began
OL,20,Fhis youth career with Carlisle United.
OL,21,FHe now plays for Manchester City.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
