OL,3,CCumbria's James Trafford and Dean
OL,4,CHenderson selected for England World
OL,5,CCup team
OL,7,F29-year-old Dean Henderson was born in
OL,8,FWhitehaven, and he also began his
OL,9,Fcareer with the Carlisle United youth
OL,10,Fteam.
OL,12,FHe joined the Manchester United
OL,13,Facademy aged 14, and he now captains
OL,14,FCrystal Palace.
OL,16,FHere is the line-up of England's 2026
OL,17,FWorld Cup team in full:
OL,19,FGoalkeepers: Jordan Pickford, Dean
OL,20,FHenderson, James Trafford
